{"parentUuid":"89724f02-c0a1-41c9-b667-c6b425d5ab79","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/my","sessionId":"9dc89b79-e651-4539-ac98-483fae1104bf","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"main","message":{"type":"message","model":"z-ai/glm4.7","usage":{"input_tokens":7241,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"claude_cache_creation_5_m_tokens":0,"claude_cache_creation_1_h_tokens":0},"role":"assistant","id":"1d4aaf1b0bce490ab2209ce656cb3b18","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想了解如何搜索某篇论文被哪些新闻媒体报道。这是一个关于研究方法的问题，我应该提供一些实用的方法和工具来帮助用户追踪论文的媒体报道情况。\n\n这不需要使用任何工具，我可以直接提供一些建议。","signature":""}]},"type":"assistant","uuid":"b8e65a66-91a7-4b8b-9101-6a682dc5e469","timestamp":"2026-03-02T07:34:05.420Z"}
{"parentUuid":"b8e65a66-91a7-4b8b-9101-6a682dc5e469","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/my","sessionId":"9dc89b79-e651-4539-ac98-483fae1104bf","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"main","message":{"type":"message","model":"z-ai/glm4.7","usage":{"input_tokens":7241,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"claude_cache_creation_5_m_tokens":0,"claude_cache_creation_1_h_tokens":0},"role":"assistant","id":"1d4aaf1b0bce490ab2209ce656cb3b18","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搜索论文媒体报道的方法有多种，以下是几种常用方式：\n\n## 1. Google Scholar\n- 在论文页面查看\"被引用数\"下方有时会显示媒体报道\n- 用论文标题 + \"news/media\" 搜索\n\n## 2. 专门的学术传播平台\n- **Altmetric** - 追踪论文在新闻媒体、博客、社交媒体上的提及\n- **EurekAlert!** - 科学新闻发布平台\n- **ScienceDaily** - 科学新闻聚合\n\n## 3. 媒体数据库/新闻搜索\n- **Google News** - 用论文标题或作者名搜索\n- **LexisNexis** - 专业新闻数据库（需订阅）\n- **Factiva** - 道琼斯新闻数据库\n\n## 4. 社交媒体搜索\n- Twitter/X用论文链接或关键词搜索\n- ResearchGate 有时显示媒体报道\n\n## 5. 大学官网\n- 论文作者所在大学的\"新闻/News\"栏目\n- 大学研究新闻稿通常会发布媒体转载\n\n## 实用搜索技巧\n```\n\"[论文标题]\" AND news\n\"[论文标题]\" AND media coverage\n\"[论文标题]\" AND press release\n\"[作者名]\" AND [大学名] news\n```\n\n您有具体的论文想搜索吗？告诉我标题我可以帮您更精确地搜索。"}]},"type":"assistant","uuid":"e54bab46-0692-4b9f-b207-79c14a7c6a61","timestamp":"2026-03-02T07:34:09.747Z"}
